<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	#set($version="2017061505")
    #set($commonUrl="https://fs.51fanbei.com/h5/app/activity/06")
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>618主会场</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/dist/activity/06/activityHome.css?version=$version">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="activityHomeWrap">
		<div class="activityHomeBanner">
			<img src="$commonUrl/bannerBg.png" class="banner">
      <span class="bannerTitle"><span class="bannerTitleCorner"></span></span>
      <div class="countDown" id="countDown">
        <h2>距离活动结束</h2>
				<span class="time_item" id="day_show"></span>
				<span class="time_item" id="hour_show"></span>
				<span class="time_item" id="minute_show"></span>
				<span class="time_item" id="second_show"></span>
			</div>
			<a class="goCoupons" href="/fanbei-web/receiveCoupons?addUiName=COUPONS"></a>
		</div>
		<div class="activityHomeContent">
			<ul class="selectedHome clearfix" id="selectedHome">
				<li data-type='1'><a href=""><img src="$commonUrl/selectedHome1.png"></a></li>
				<li data-type='2'><a href=""><img src="$commonUrl/selectedHome2.png"></a></li>
				<li data-type='3'><a href=""><img src="$commonUrl/selectedHome3.png"></a></li>
				<li data-type='4'><a href="strollHome"><img src="$commonUrl/selectedHome4.png"></a></li>
			</ul>
			<div class="boutiqueHome">
				<h2 id="goodTitle"></h2>
				<ul id="qualityGoodsList"></ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
    <div id="alert" class="alert">
        <p class="getState">福利通知</p>
        <div class="getCon">

            <p style="text-align: center">6-18 13:30 — 6-19 13:30</p>
			<p style="margin: .1rem auto;text-align: center;">满减不给力  返现更钜惠</p>
            <p style="text-align: center">苹果手机的用户暂时无法在下单时直接享受满减券以及分期免息功能，
			相应的优惠会在您交易完成确认后以返利形式返现到您账户</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tryAgain"  onclick="close()">开始抢购</div>
    </div>
    <div id="shadow" onclick="close()"></div>
	<script>
        if(getBlatFrom()==2){
            var ver=getInfo().appVersion;
            if(ver&&ver<364){
                $('.alert').fadeIn();
                $('#shadow').fadeIn();
            }
        }
        $('#alert').on('click',function close() {
            $('.alert').hide();
            $('#shadow').hide();
        })
	</script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/dist/activity/06/activityHome.js?version=$version"></script>
</body>
</html>
